  "title": "UTC日期 第1部分",
  "group": "处理日期",
  "options": [
    {
      "text": "Wed, 01 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT"
    },
    {
      "text": "Thu, 02 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT"
    },
    {
      "text": "TypeError"
    },
    {
      "text": "NaN"
    }
  ],
  "objectives": [],
  "questionProse": [
    "输出将包含什么？"
  ],
  "hintsProse": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "你会得到 `TypeError: date.toUTCString is not a function`，因为 [`Date.UTC()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/UTC) 返回的是毫秒整数而非日期实例。\n\n      {/* [`getFullYear()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getFullYear) 方法会使用你的本地时区偏移（假设这些题目中为 GMT-07:00）\n      这意味着它会给出前一年（新年夜-7小时）。\n      [`getUTCFullYear()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getUTCFullYear) 方法会返回我们通过 `Date.UTC()` 提供的年份，即 2020。\n      */}"
  ]
}
```
